cgcloud__Vehicle__c.name: cgcloud__Vehicle__c
cgcloud__Vehicle__c.description: Stores the details of the vehicle object.

LastReferencedDate.description: Most recent date on which a user referenced this record.

LastViewedDate.description: Most recent date on which a user viewed this record.

cgcloud__Description__c.description: Reference to the description based on the user-specified language.

cgcloud__License_Plate_Number__c.description: License plate number of the vehicle.

cgcloud__Sales_Org__c.description: Describes the sales org to which the vehicle belongs

cgcloud__Vehicle_Type__c.description: Specifies the vehicle specific speed profiles that are used in the external ptv tool for route optimization.
